column5: Quick trip to st clair as the winds looked good.  Bimini made it possible 30* and full sun.  All trolling , too hot to cast.  2/2 and great boat rides.  Didn’t put many hours in. Just nice to get out.
Nice fish!  Still a muskie destination I need to get to.
nice shootin...flippin those docks yesterday at 2pm at the CBAF clubby, on the leeward side of the lake...ouch
Nice report Glen.  Multiple muskie days are always nice.
Must of swallowed the fly I tied. LMAO  NICE FISH GUYS
We didn’t get to use any flies this trip.   	I caught my fish on a (basement bait) I had custom made for st clair though.  I always enjoy custom lures.
